1.00	Helen_the_Authoress_(1967_The_Andy_Griffith_Show_episode)	Helen, the Authoress	"Helen, the Authoress" is an episode from the American television program The Andy Griffith Show broadcast Monday, February 27, 1967 on CBS. Helen's sudden celebrity as an author creates a rift in her relationship with Andy. "Helen, the Authoress" was the 24th episode in the show's seventh season, and the 213th episode in the complete series.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/08/HTA_03.JPG/200px-HTA_03.JPG
